<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Give thanks
 With a grateful heart
 Give thanks
 To the Holy one
 Give thanks
 Because He's given
 Jesus Christ His son.

[V2]
 And now let the weak say
 I am strong
 Let the poor say
 I am rich
 Because of what
 The Lord has done
 For us.</lyrics>
<title>Give Thanks</title>
<author>Coro Scuole David</author>
<hymn_number>98</hymn_number>
</song>